snippet.title: LUSHFOIL PHOTOGRAPHY SIM | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Lushfoil Photography Sim is a tranquil exploration and photography experience featuring realistic in-game cameras and a vast selection of faithfully-detailed landscapes presented in stunning visual fidelity. Coming soon to PC and consoles. Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1749860?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=AIShowcase2023&utm_medium=web

Developed by Matt Newell. Published by Annapurna Interactive. 

© Annapurna Interactive, 2023
